Dear friends around the world: We’ve danced together so many times, and now we need your help. The attack on Supernova has affected us deeply. While hundreds of our loved ones suffer irreparable damage and many still hostage in Gaza, we are committed to using the power of music to help. Help us #BringThemBack by grabbing the compilation featuring our new track called “kiss my baby” and limited edition tshirt - your support counts! All proceeds go to support the survivors, from rehabilitation to aid in returning the hostages. Link in bio or visit www.october07.org 🤍

We believe that music has the power to heal, and we want to thank the global music community for your overwhelming support for this project. It means more than you can imagine in these challenging days for humanity. 
50+ artists from all colors of the electronic music rainbow together in one compilation. 
Get the music and help us help our Supernova family. 
Visit october07.org or @Emc_Bring_Them_back
